headline: TE Connectivity to hold annual general meeting of shareholders on March 11, 2026
summary: TE Connectivity plc (NYSE: TEL) will hold its 2026 annual general meeting of shareholders (AGM) on March 11, 2026, at 2 p.m. GMT at the Conrad Dublin, Earlsfort Terrace, Dublin, Ireland. Shareholders who are registered with voting rights in the share register of TE as of the close of business (EST) on Jan. 8, 2026, (the record date) will be entitled to vote on the matters presented at the AGM.
